Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓您先死一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先死一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒心丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您吃下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒心丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的咒印等級目前是狀態一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個藥丸可以強迫咒印的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒到狀態二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了狀態二後 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印侵蝕身體的速度會急劇上升
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聞不問的話 很快就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想控制狀態二的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須長時間讓身體習慣它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待身體適應後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會得到和我們一樣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒後 只能撐幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定會死亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸 音忍四人眾的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了以後會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是為此而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們的結界忍術可以把副作用壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將永遠的死緩和成假死狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的結界忍術值得相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來就是大蛇丸大人的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界 防禦壁忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印 封印術是我們所擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我現在還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們再磨蹭的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助大人真的會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四黑霧陣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封黑法印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 暫時告一段落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到任務拖了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷同 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人 不 是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是大蛇丸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從方向來看 你們是從木葉返回的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大桶裡面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是兩個上忍 有點吃力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有咒印啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可不會像上次被你們偷襲的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸的玩具 別小看了木葉的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 靜音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷同 弦間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆居然會被打成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒只能做些應急處理…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 伊瓦西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超出了忍術的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人去追 只是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦間 別說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括佐助在內的那五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和另外兩個人的氣味發生了衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是五人已經遠離了血腥味了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 有人在慫恿佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快追佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事是鹿丸來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副老大下令的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到血腥味 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們恐怕戰鬥過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去現場也許能得到一些情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能貿然接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就轉為偵察模式 緩緩接近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來佐助可就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過火之國的國境了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去追佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於剛才的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒也會變得嚴密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是\N忍者追殺部隊的人和他們發生了衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現敵人設下埋伏或陷阱的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起 大家注意聽和看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遭遇埋伏前把那些傢伙找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 一旦發現可疑的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅要避開 還要告知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到他們之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的絕招把他們打個落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次見到他都會增加些新的招數啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為趕上他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前邊飄散著敵人的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另外五張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這形狀 是結界法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種陷阱忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法陣系的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是敵人進入\N符咒圍起來的法陣內便啟動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種時間差陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從我老爸的書裡看到的一種高級忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繞路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 你去做你該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 你現在還不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你是個愛亂來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術才剛結束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼心急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡早修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也… 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉並不只是身體的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論再怎麼不幸也要能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是一種修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂來的話 傷勢會惡化的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我調配的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個喝下 先把身體養好 小李
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始就步步陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 敵人似乎也沒多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱設得很顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳下有繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別絆到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子模仿術…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 都讓你小心一點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然其中一根繩索反射了陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易發現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而另一根繩索塗成了消光的綠色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉眼難以察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明急著趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還設下如此精密的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個陷阱呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一定要把佐助帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就讓我的新絕招大展身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少安毋躁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的作戰準備結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去接觸目標
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 時間很緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還要在這裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以狀態二來戰鬥 消耗太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最麻煩的是暫時沒辦法用力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我們剛才遭遇了兩個上忍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不使出全力 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幹掉的就是我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果碰到那種情況 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別錯過製造煙霧的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們還沒有發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來在那個棺桶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上邊似乎有結界 無法透視
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們那麼想得到佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會輕易殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也能算隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在的狀況真夠頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是能行就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明起來很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 你煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別理他們 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的必殺螺旋丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:22:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然內訌 鹿丸小隊大危機
